From cd04d2bf7a6453745880d0f6b0c05344008f755a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hiren Mehta <hiren.mehta@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 09:39:51 -0700
Subject: drivers/edac: Add Salina EDAC support

Port Salina EDAC support from zephyr to linux. The Salina EDAC
driver is similar to Elba and relies on device-tree nodes installed by
u-boot.

Signed-off-by: Hiren Mehta <hiren.mehta@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Amruta Jandhyala <amruta.jandhyala@amd.com>
---
